程序包 main.com.ae2dms

类 Level

java.lang.Object
main.com.ae2dms.Level
所有已实现的接口:
java.lang.Iterable<GameObject>, IMessage
public final class Level
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<GameObject>, IMessage
The Level class is about controlling each levels.The class has two GameGrid components, one is diamond grid and the other is a grid containing objects other than diamonds. This class monitors the positions of all the objects on the map by changing objects' positions on corresponding grids and check whether the level is completed

    • toString

      public java.lang.String toString()
      Combine the two game grids: objectGrid and diamondGrid into one string for print and write. First get the string format of both grids by using GameGrid.toString(). Next, get all the indexes of the diamonds in the diamondGrid string. Then, replacing all the char at these extracted indexes in the objectGrid string with 'D',if the object on target position is not crate. If it is crate_on_diamond situation, the target object will be set as 'o',crate_on_diamond. The same logic for keeper_on_wall and keeper_on_diamond situations
      覆盖:
      toString 在类中 java.lang.Object
      返回:
      return a string contains the layouts of crates,walls, floors,diamonds and keeper of current level.
